  THE ONLY BASEBALL GAME THAT MATTERS! The biggest baseball video game 
  launch to date! Major League Baseball 2K6 is THE official destination 
  for the MLB experience on every major home console. Major League Baseball 
  2K6 delivers the most authentic and immersive baseball experience, bringing 
  the pitcher batter experience to a new level of authenticity on all platforms. 
  Major League Baseball 2K6 features The World Baseball Classic which will be 
  an "exclusive" playable mode in-game.
  
  * Pitcher / Batter Showdown -- A revolutionary breakthrough in batting control 
    coupled with a new and intuitive pitching interface and truly accurate and 
    individual player behavior brings the pitcher batter experience to a new level. 

  * Exclusive World Baseball Classic Mode û 16 teams, tournament structure and 
    uniforms, logos and locations. All the excitement of this brand new international 
    tournament exclusively captured in Major League Baseball 2K6. 

  * All-New Movement Model û Running, throwing, fielding, tag outs and player to player 
    collision animations have been re-built bringing an incredible look and feel to 
    the game. 

  * Umpire Challenges û New, Interactive umpire arguments directly affect team moral 
    and ratings. 

  * Flashbacks (Xbox, Xbox 360 and PS2 with HDD) û Big plays and at-bats will be recalled 
    at the end of innings and subsequent key at-bats. 

  * Player Morale System û Team ratings revolve around situation specific decisions made 
    by GM. 

  * V.I.P. (Virtual Identity Profile) - Save your friends' profiles to compete when they're 
    not available! Learn their tendencies, moves, & logic for more heated battles. Get the 
    upper hand in an online tournaments by downloading other players' VIP profiles. 

    
        
